author: Hank Long
title: St. Paul’s Urban Growler has a new landlord
text:
Apartment Sales Tracker Home / News / St. Paul’s Urban Growler has a new landlord The Urban Growler has called 2325 Endicott St. in St. Paul its home since its August 2014 opening. Longtime tenant Deneen Pottery purchased the century-old building this month. Staff photo: Bill Klotz St. Paul’s Urban Growler has a new landlord By: Hank Long Hank Long October 26, 2015 7:00 am 0 The new landlord is a family-run pottery business founded by Peter Deneen in 1972.
